data.description: OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS YOUR CLOSING COSTS! This SOLAR POWERED 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts 2,423 square feet, this gem redefines modern luxury. As you step inside, you'll immediately be greeted by the grandeur of the huge foyer setting the tone for the entire home. The living room is a true showcase of sophistication, featuring custom black roller shades that add a touch of elegance and privacy to the space. But that's not all – a custom-built TV and electric fireplace with ambient lighting create the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings spent with loved ones. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort and relaxation, offering a custom cordless honeycomb room darkening shade, ensuring you can enjoy a peaceful night's sleep at any time of day. Entertaining guests is a breeze with the wet bar, which includes a designer backsplash and a beverage fridge. One of the most striking features of this home is the handmade chandelier imported all the way from Ecuador, adding a touch of international flair and sophistication to the dining area. Movie nights will be a hit in the dedicated media room, providing the perfect space for cinematic experiences in the comfort of your own home.For the tech-savvy homeowner, the living area features Alexa Echo next-generation voice control, seamlessly integrated with recessed ceiling speakers, allowing you to control your home environment with just your voice. Step outside and unwind on the extended covered privacy patio, the ideal spot for al fresco dining or lounging while enjoying the beautiful surroundings. If you're looking for a more intimate setting, the front privacy screened sitting area provides a peaceful retreat.This home is a true gem, combining thoughtful design, high-quality finishes, and modern technology to create a haven of comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and experience the pinnacle of luxury living. Welcome home!
